<H3> <TI>   19 Russians Among 100 Leaving Yemen </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    19 Russians Among 100 Leaving Yemen </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD1105121694 Moscow ITAR-TASS in English 1112 GMT 11 May 94 </F>
<F P=103> LD1105121694 </F>
<F P=104>  Moscow ITAR-TASS </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

<F P=106> [By ITAR-TASS correspondent Roman Zadunayskiy] </F>
  [Text] Moscow May 11 TASS -- 100 foreigners, including 19 
Russians, will leave Yemen aboard a Russian plane which left for 
Djibouti on Wednesday. 
  The foreigners were evacuated from Yemen and are now 
awaiting 
the plane aboard two Russian vessels docked in Djibouti -- the 
"Nikolay Tikhonov" and the "Khudozhnik Kustodiyev". 
  TASS was told by the Russian Ministry for Emergency 
Situations that the evacuation of Russians from Yemen is 
expected to be completed by the end of the week. 

</TEXT>

