<H3> <TI>   Government Delegation Ends Visit to France </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Government Delegation Ends Visit to France </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD1105122994 Riga Radio Riga Network in Latvian 0900 GMT 11 
May 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD1105122994 </F>
