<H3> <TI>   Reportage on State Duma Budget Bill Debate </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Reportage on State Duma Budget Bill Debate </PHRASE></F></HT>
<H4>    Adopts Draft Law on Federal Budget </H4>

<F P=102> LD1105122294 Moscow ITAR-TASS in English 1108 GMT 11 May 94 </F>
<F P=103> LD1105122294 </F>
<F P=104>  Moscow ITAR-TASS </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

<F P=106> [By BUSINESS-TASS] </F>
  [Text] Moscow May 11 TASS -- The State Duma has adopted in 
the first reading a draft law on federal budget. 
  Under the law, federal budgetary expenditures were endorsed 
at 193.3 trillion roubles and revenues - at 124.4 trillion 
roubles. 
  The top limit of the budget deficit was established to reach 
the amount equivalent to 35.6 per cent of budgetary expenditures 
for the current year. 

</TEXT>

</DOC>

