<F P=100> Regional Affairs </F>
<H3> <TI>   Southern Metals Giant Shuts Down for Want of Capital </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Southern Metals Giant Shuts Down for Want of Capital </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   PM1105113594 Moscow IZVESTIYA in Russian 11 May 94 p 1 </F>
<F P=103> PM1105113594 </F>
