<H3> <TI>   Chuvashia To Become Tax Free Zone for 3 Years </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Chuvashia To Become Tax Free Zone for 3 Years </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD1205163294 Moscow Radiostantsiya Ekho Moskvy in Russian 
1100 GMT 12 May 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD1205163294 </F>
<F P=104>  Moscow Radiostantsiya Ekho Moskvy </F>
<F P=105>  Russian </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Chuvashia is to become a taxfree zone for three 
years. In accordance with an edict issued by republican 
President Fedorov, all enterprises and organizations which 
produce consumer goods and technical equipment will be exempt 
from income tax. Banks and insurance companies will also pay 
lower taxes. 

</TEXT>

